{"word":"G4298 - προκόπτω - prokóptō - prok-op'-to - Increase","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προκόπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prokóptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prok-op'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Increase</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விருத்தியடை, தேறு, பலப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to lengthen out by hammering"},{"paragraph":"2. to go forward, advance, proceed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2875 - κόπτω - kóptō - kop'-to/2875\">G2875</a>; to <i>drive forward</i> (as if by beating), that is, (figuratively and intransitively) to <i>advance</i> (in amount, to <i>grow</i>; in time, to <i>be well along</i>): - increase, proceed, profit, be far spent, wax.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4297/4297\">G4297</a>, <a href=\"#/G4298/4298\">G4298</a>"}]}